---
---
<section data-test="how-it-works" style="padding:4rem 1.5rem;border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);">
  <div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;">
    <h2 style="font-size:0.75rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">How It Works</h2>
    <h3 style="font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3vw,2rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--color-text);max-width:600px;margin-bottom:3rem;">
      Four skills drive every workflow, from first idea to shipped product.
    </h3>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:0;border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;">
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;border-right:1px solid var(--color-border);">
        <code data-test="skill-name" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--color-accent);display:block;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">/rs-init</code>
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.6;">Initialise a project with a RootSpec scaffold — spec directory, hooks, and CI config.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;border-right:1px solid var(--color-border);">
        <code data-test="skill-name" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--color-accent);display:block;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">/rs-spec</code>
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.6;">Interview-driven spec authoring. Philosophy → Truths → Interactions → Systems → Stories.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;border-right:1px solid var(--color-border);">
        <code data-test="skill-name" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--color-accent);display:block;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">/rs-impl</code>
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.6;">Test-driven implementation. User stories become Cypress tests; code must make them pass.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1.5rem;">
        <code data-test="skill-name" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--color-accent);display:block;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">/rs-validate</code>
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.6;">Full spec-to-code audit. Generates a report linking every test result back to its story.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
